query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS logs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  app_id INT NOT NULL,
  level VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'info',
  message TEXT NOT NULL,
  context JSON,
  user_id VARCHAR(100),
  device_id VARCHAR(100),
  ip VARCHAR(50),
  created_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
